# Overlord Local Workflow

- Attach first: `ovld protocol attach --ticket-id $TICKET_ID`
- Update during work: `ovld protocol update --session-key <sessionKey> --ticket-id $TICKET_ID --summary "..." --phase execute`
- Ask when blocked: `ovld protocol ask --session-key <sessionKey> --ticket-id $TICKET_ID --question "..."`
- Deliver last: `ovld protocol deliver --session-key <sessionKey> --ticket-id $TICKET_ID --payload-file -`

Always include `changeRationales` on delivery for meaningful behavioral file changes.
